even_numbers array: contains all even numbers in order. Initialize:

odd_front = 1

odd_back = len_odd (number of odd numbers) even_front = 1

even_back = len_even

Then, for each row i from 1 to n:

   if i is odd:

      for j=1 to div:

          take odd_front element (odd_numbers(odd_front)), then even_back element (even_numbers(even_back)). increment odd_front by 1, decrement even_back by 1.

   else:

      for j=1 to div:

          take even_front element (even_numbers(even_front)), then odd_back element (odd_numbers(odd_back)).
